---
title: Sweet Ponzu Pork & Bok Choy Wraps Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: These wraps are packed with saucy ponzu pork, tender bok choy and cabbage, and fluffy rice,  for the perfect on-the-go meal. Sriracha mayo and a sprinkle of crispy fried onions add a hit of heat and crunch to every bite, while a side of mixed greens tossed with sesame dressing keeps things fresh.

